# SQLite authoring DB — gitignored build artifact, rebuilt from the committed
# NDJSON source (site/db/ndjson/) by `pnpm db:build`. The NDJSON is the tracked
# source of truth; the .db never lands in git.
caail.db
caail.db-journal
caail.db-wal
caail.db-shm

